      right: ["Atrial fibrillation with rapid ventricular response from untreated thyrotoxicosis","Thyroid storm post-RAI: extreme tachycardia, fever, altered mental status — EMERGENCY","Airway compromise from large goiter or substernal extension","New-onset heart failure precipitated by uncontrolled hyperthyroidism in elderly patient","Suspicious nodule on ultrasound requiring FNA to exclude malignancy","Tracheal deviation or compression from massive goiter"]
